== About me
I'm a Ph.D. student in the Department of Computer Science and Engineering at Michigan State University. I am fortunately advised by [http://www.cse.msu.edu/~tangjili/ Prof. Jiliang Tang] in the [http://dse.cse.msu.edu/ DSE lab].


== Research
My research interests include, but not limited to the following areas: 
- Graph Neural Network
- Natural Language Processing
- Knowledge Graph
- Applying graph representation learning to scientific domains, e.g., single cell, spatial transcriptomics

== Open-Source Projects
- DANCE: A Deep Learning Library and Benchmark Platform for Single-Cell Analysis \n
[https://github.com/OmicsML/dance Github]  [https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2022.10.19.512741v2 Paper]  [https://arxiv.org/abs/2210.12385 Survey]  [https://github.com/OmicsML/awesome-deep-learning-single-cell-papers Reading List]

